((lambda () ;; æœ€åŸºæœ¬çš„å¿«é€Ÿæ’åºï¼Œç”¨äºéªŒè¯ä¸€ç­‰å‡½æ•°ã€åˆ—è¡¨æ“ä½œã€ifã€and/orç­‰ç‰¹æ®Šç»“æ„
;; æ­¤æ’åºç®—æ³•æ— æ³•å¤„ç†é‡å¤å…ƒç´ 

(define filter
  (lambda (f lst)
    (if (null? lst)
        '()
        (if (f (car lst))
            (cons (car lst) (filter f (cdr lst)))
            (filter f (cdr lst))))))

(define concat
  (lambda (a b)
    (if (null? a)
        b
        (cons (car a) (concat (cdr a) b)))))

(define quicksort
  (lambda (array)
    (if (or (null? array) (null? (cdr array)))
        array
        (concat (quicksort (filter (lambda (x)
                                     (if (< x (car array)) #t #f))
                                   array))
                           (cons (car array)
                                 (quicksort (filter (lambda (x)
                                                      (if (> x (car array)) #t #f))
                                                    array)))))))
))
